<StatusCodes
  id={undefined}
  label={undefined}
  responses={{
    "200": {
      description:
        "Returns the downloadable file or binary PDF data of the AgreementGen document.",
      content: {

          schema: {
            type: "object",

                type: "string",

          },
        },
        "application/pdf": {
          schema: { type: "string", format: "binary" },
